---
title: Spicy Fish Taco Grill Packets Foil packet meals for the campfire or grill
description: These flavorful fish tacos are total *fire emoji*! You’ll place a foil packet of tilapia, pepper, and onion over hot coals (or in an oven), warm up flour tortillas, and load all that goodness right in. A tangy slaw makes a perfect topping, and a finish flourish of smoky red pepper crema and a squeeze of fresh lime brings it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6682ea0988a40e5df74250b3-8193c156.jpeg
